data.description: *** OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY NOV 4TH 2-4 PM *** Welcome to 24732 Buck Creek, nestled within the gated community of Two Creeks! This stunning 3,013 square foot home, built in 2013 by Ryland, offers a perfect blend of modern elegance and functionality. With 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, a dedicated office, a formal dining room, a game room, and a wealth of upgrades, it's the epitome of comfortable, and updated contemporary living. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting extended entryway that leads you into an open floor plan, creating a sense of spaciousness. The large windows allow an abundance of natural light to flood the living space, giving the interior a bright and airy ambiance. The heart of the home is the eat-in kitchen, complete with an island featuring a breakfast bar, perfect for casual dining or entertaining guests. The kitchen boasts a Reverse Osmosis (RO) system, a new vent hood, upgraded kitchen range, and faucets. The new wood floors throughout the house provide an elegant touch. The private master suite offers a tranquil retreat, with an ensuite bathroom featuring a renovated walk-in shower, and an extended vanity. Upstairs, you'll discover a spacious game room in the loft area, perfect for family fun and entertainment. Additionally, there are three other bedrooms, one with an ensuite, ensuring everyone has their own space. All full bathrooms feature a bidet and each shower has a hose combo. Stepping outside, you'll find a covered patio and an extra seating area in the backyard, perfect for enjoying the outdoors. The back yard backs to a green space, offering plenty of privacy and a serene backdrop for your outdoor gatherings. The low-maintenance lawn enhances the convenience of the exterior space. This home comes with numerous upgrades, including a new roof installed in 2020, a new garage door and garage opener, a new HVAC compressor, and solar panels that significantly reduce your electric bill with normal consumption. Additionally, a water softener was added in 2019, as well as custom solar blinds. Two Creeks is a gated neighborhood that offers a sense of security and community. Residents also have access to the neighborhood pool, a great place to cool off during the Texas summers. The location is superb, with quick and easy access to I-10, making your daily commute a breeze. Plus, it's part of the highly-rated Northside Independent School District, ensuring excellent educational opportunities for your family. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite Buck Creek residence your new home sweet home in the heart of Two Creeks!
